io.honeycomb

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.honeycomb.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores a Builder and some metadata, executes all dynamic fields upon instantiation, and can enqueue HTTP requests to Transmission.
